title: 3 and Out - Jimmy G/Niners Reaction,  Final Cuts, Wentz Expectations, Dolphins Hype
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Jimmy G/Niners Reaction,  Final Cuts, Wentz Expectations, Dolphins Hype
description:
John reacts to the surprise news of Jimmy Garoppolo re-signing with the Niners, if Trey Lance is in trouble, the 3 types of players that teams will be cutting in final cut downs, what are realistic expectations for Carson Wentz in DC, why he’s noy buying the hype around the revamped Dolphins, and what CFB programs face the most pressure entering the 2022 season.
